sequenceDiagram
  participant Client as Web/Native client
  participant API as services/api
  participant Runtime as services/ai-runtime
  participant Tools as Starlog tools
  participant Store as Persistent store

  Client->>API: Submit message, capture context, or confirmation
  API->>Store: Append thread message and create/resume run
  API->>Runtime: Start run with thread snapshot and policy
  Runtime->>Runtime: Select prompt, provider, tools, fallback path
  Runtime->>Tools: Request typed tool call or guarded action
  Tools->>API: Persist tool result, interrupt, or candidate write
  API->>Store: Store run step and surface event
  API-->>Client: Stream/poll typed message parts and panels
  Client->>API: Confirm or reject major write
  API->>Store: Persist confirmation and final run state
